{"type":"message","id":"f03960c1","parentId":"9e3a3c1d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:11:39.838Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hoiuta1d706e_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 151114\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: research/strategy_c_hybrid_scoring.py (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state:\r\n\r\n1. Phase 1 advancement completed with CFI Compression Experiment\r\n2. Key finding: CFI ≥ 0.5 AND freq ∈ [3, 120) is the three-dimensional filter\r\n3. Next pending: Hybrid CFI×Freq scoring experiment (Strategy C)\r\n4. Formula: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n\r\nThe immediate next action from the pending list is to run the Hybrid CFI×Freq scoring experiment. This involves:\r\n- Implementing the scoring formula: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n- Testing if this distinguishes \"constant format\" (freq≈160, CFI=1) from \"research trajectory\" (freq<120, CFI>0.5)\r\n- Running 200 pulses, 80/20 split, compare against binary thresholds\r\n\r\nI should create a concrete experiment script that implements this. Looking at the previous experiment structure, it was in `research/CFI_COMPRESSION_SYNTHESIS.md`. This next experiment would be Strategy C.\r\n\r\nLet me create a mutation that sets up the next experiment - likely creating a new experiment script or updating the synthesis document with the new experiment plan.\r\n\r\nActually, looking at the workflow, I should create a new experiment script that implements Strategy C with the hybrid scoring formula. This is the most concrete next step.\r\n\r\nLet me create an experiment script `research/strategy_c_experiment.ps1` that:\r\n1. Loads the pulse data\r\n2. Computes score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120) for each token\r\n3. Ranks tokens by score\r\n4. Evaluates precision/recall against ground truth\r\n5. Compares to binary threshold approach\r\n\r\nThis advances the pending \"Hybrid CFI×Freq scoring experiment\" goal.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe CFI Compression Synthesis identified Strategy C (hybrid CFI×Freq scoring) as the next experiment, but no implementation script exists yet. The formula score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120) needs to be tested against binary thresholds to see if it better distinguishes constant-format tokens from research trajectory.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate experiment script implementing Strategy C hybrid scoring, following the structure from the successful CFI compression experiment.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Strategy C: Hybrid CFI×Freq Scoring Experiment\r\n# Test: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n# Hypothesis: Penalizes constant-format (freq=160, CFI=1) while preserving research trajectory\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$SampleSize = 200,\r\n    [float]$TrainSplit = 0.8\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\r\n$results = @{}\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"=== Strategy C: Hybrid CFI×Freq Scoring ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\n\r\n# Load pulse corpus\r\n$pulses = Get-Content \"corpus/pulses.json\" | ConvertFrom-Json\r\n$sample = $pulses | Get-Random -Count ([Math]::Min($SampleSize, $pulses.Count))\r\n\r\n# Token frequency map\r\n$freq = @{}\r\n# CFI map  \r\n$cfi = @{}\r\n\r\nforeach ($p in $sample) {\r\n    foreach ($t in $p.tokens) {\r\n        $freq[$t]++\r\n    }\r\n    foreach ($e in $p.events) {\r\n        $cfi[$e.token] = $e.cfi\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Compute hybrid score: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n$scores = @{}\r\nforeach ($t in $freq.Keys) {\r\n    $f = $freq[$t]\r\n    $c = if ($cfi.ContainsKey($t)) { $cfi[$t] } else { 0 }\r\n    $scores[$t] = $c * [Math]::Min(1, $f / 120.0)\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Load ground truth (research tokens from training set)\r\n$trainSize = [int]($sample.Count * $TrainSplit)\r\n$trainPulses = $sample[0..($trainSize-1)]\r\n$testPulses = $sample[$trainSize..($sample.Count-1)]\r\n\r\n# Build ground truth from training pulses\r\n$gtTokens = @{}\r\nforeach ($p in $trainPulses) {\r\n    foreach ($t in $p.research_tokens) {\r\n        $gtTokens[$t] = $true\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Test Strategy C: Top 50 tokens by hybrid score\r\n$topByScore = $scores.GetEnumerator() | Sort-Object -Descending Value | Select-Object -First 50\r\n\r\n# Precision/Recall calculation\r\n$truePositives = 0\r\n$falsePositives = 0\r\nforeach ($entry in $topByScore) {\r\n    if ($gtTokens.ContainsKey($entry.Key)) { $truePositives++ } else { $falsePositives++ }\r\n}\r\n\r\n$strategyC = @{\r\n    Precision = if (($truePositives + $falsePositives) -gt 0) { $truePositives / ($truePositives + $falsePositives) } else { 0 }\r\n    Recall = if ($gtTokens.Count -gt 0) { $truePositives / $gtTokens.Count } else { 0 }\r\n    TruePositives = $truePositives\r\n    FalsePositives = $falsePositives\r\n    Method = \"Hybrid CFI×min(1,freq/120)\"\r\n}\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"Strategy C Results:\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\r\nWrite-Host \"  Precision: $($strategyC.Precision.ToString('F4'))\"\r\nWrite-Host \"  Recall: $($strategyC.Recall.ToString('F4'))\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 15:11:34\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774379499837}}
{"type":"message","id":"cfbb0d5a","parentId":"f03960c1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:11:47.917Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The pulse script ran and created a mutation for the Strategy C experiment. Let me report this concisely.","thinkingSignature":"7a2367d23fa998d3f4476d1f2f62eb339c018f6cdc27eb1201f1785f86917307"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n**Sandbox Pulse — 2026-03-24 15:11 UTC**\n\n**6 files changed**, 298 insertions(+), 86 deletions(-):\n- `memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 151114.md` — pulse log created\n- `mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 151114.mutation` — new mutation created\n- `mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 151014.mutation` — previous proposal auto-rejected (superseded)\n\n**What happened:** The CFI Compression Synthesis flagged Strategy C as the next experiment but no script existed yet. The pulse created an implementation script that tests the hybrid scoring formula:\n\n> `score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)`\n\nThis scores tokens by combining their CFI value with a frequency dampener — designed to penalize constant-format tokens (freq≈160, CFI=1 → score caps at ~1.0) while preserving research trajectory tokens that have moderate frequency but lower CFI. The experiment computes precision/recall against the training set ground truth.\n\n**Status:** Mutation proposed and awaiting review. No conflicts — the previous proposal was auto-rejected in favor of this one."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2080,"output":283,"cacheRead":12245,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14608,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774379499839}}
